BIC:

CYCLONUS looked at HYDRAS inquisitively. "Sir, the ship is nearly
rebuilt, except for propulsion." He paused thoughtfully, as if going
over things in his mind. "We have weapons, shields, sensors, power,
life support - with the exception of a few small jobs we have
everything except for flight capability."

There was another thoughtful pause from CYCLONUS, "Did you want us to
attmpt those as well? The propulsion units is what took the heaviest
damage in the crash landing of this ship, and what will require the
most work, it will require signifigant resources."

As Hydras and CYCLONUS enter the hanger bay DEEPSTRYKE strightened.
"Attention!" he called out as the rest of Hydras' troops also
strightened and presented themsleves for his inspection.

"Troops ready for inspection sir!' DEEPSTRYKE called out to HYDRAS as
he saluted both HYDRAS and CYCLONUS.

Behind DEEPSTRYKE stood the other members of HYDRAS' troops,
BLACKRAZOR, PHOBIA, INSECTICON, BRUTICUS-X, IGUANUS, TARANTULUS,
FRACTYL, INFERNO, SKYSHADOW, INJECTOR, BUZZCLAW, TERRORGATOR,
QUICKSTRIKE and WASPINATOR. The oly ones that were missing were
SCOURGE who was in the security section watching over the ship, and a
few sweeps who were flying perimter watches outside and lastly
TERRORSAUR was still missing.
